{"tid":1297510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今晚，都幾肯定狼來了係玩鳩自己友多過撚狗","createTime":"2019-07-08T15:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:21.000Z","uid":131731,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"baa238e080520c3b2fa34dd7df5e1c8561af696f","tid":1297510,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"啲狗真係隨便都check到係真定假<br />\n<br />\n反而啲真心熱血巴打絲打就畀你地fake撚咗出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲非常時期一個唔覺意畀狗逗又會少咗戰力<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係噉樣玩係會令大家挷手挷腳，訊息傳播差咗，正中港共下懷，同時亦會令抗爭失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩各位推返哂啲實際認真post上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8f489b7350afe9618c5dc037b2828cc1b87d5c","tid":1297510,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9266e7c8596aee42d36d31d5e16cbdea4d16fb37","tid":1297510,"uid":202511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95315f775455940d13cd2a2e938305e9d29dea8d","tid":1297510,"uid":210612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"黑警係狗都唔撚係蠢<br />\n你估班仆街唔撚知假膠咩<br />\n但訊息人傳人就好撚易出事"},{"pid":"ae504c2ed433b3721e49aae98525d61366805f4e","tid":1297510,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"350eff1d239d326c85ee4af7c41415b64eaae259","tid":1297510,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1296909/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1296909/page/1